sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client (SWA)
    participant API as Azure Functions
    participant Queue as Storage Queue
    participant Agent as Movie Rating Agent
    participant Blob as Blob Storage

    Client->>API: POST /api/jobs { topic: "Heat" }
    API->>Blob: Write request.json + meta.json (Queued)
    API->>Queue: Enqueue jobId
    API-->>Client: 202 Accepted { jobId }

    Queue->>API: Queue trigger fires
    API->>Blob: Update meta.json (Running)
    API->>Agent: RunAsync(request)

    Note over Agent: Title Resolution
    Note over Agent: Fan-out: 3 Scorers in parallel
    Note over Agent: Fan-in + ProsConsRollup
    Note over Agent: WeightedScoreRollup

    Agent-->>API: JobResponse (score, reasoning, pros, cons)
    API->>Blob: Write response.json + meta.json (Completed)

    loop Poll every 2s
        Client->>API: GET /api/jobs/{jobId}
        API->>Blob: Read meta.json
        API-->>Client: { meta: { Status: "Running" } }
    end

    Client->>API: GET /api/jobs/{jobId}
    API->>Blob: Read meta.json + response.json
    API-->>Client: { meta: { Status: "Completed" }, result: { score: 90, ... } }
